        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "晴跟我们讲述了她们的遭遇……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl002PF201",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "九夜吊在狂风飘摇的树上，身受长矛刺伤。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl002PF202",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我被当作奥丁的祭品，自己献祭给自己，在无人知晓的大树上！",
