    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl014aPF1",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "周六 白天 商业街",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl014aPF301",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果那天，我没有听从家族的安排，而是去赴约，瑟瑞斯就不会丢失全部的过去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl014aPF302",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对此我很愧疚。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl014aPF303",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可是，没有如果。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl014aPF304",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这三年，我一直在思考，我真正想做的是什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl014aPF305",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不再违背自己的心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl014aPF306",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我是个自私的人，从来都是。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtGirl014aPF307",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH2ST101",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从明亮的环境进入昏暗地底，我的眼睛一时无法适应，什么也看不见。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH2ST102",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我一边轻轻呼唤芬妮和星期三，一边努力适应这种黑暗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH2ST103",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“砰”一声枪响。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH2ST104",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "紧接着是疑似肉体倒地的声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH2EP301",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
