        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "失去锚定的记忆被浪潮席卷而去，",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP1K05",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只留下满怀愤懑的躯壳，",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP1K06",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "用手指在湿润的沙中雕刻。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP3K66",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在压抑、窒息的等待中，我们等来了一位出人意料的支援者。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP4K09",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "警告",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP5K18",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "神秘标记最终将我们引向一座巨大的桥。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP5K19",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在桥下，海浪一次又一次，无望地迎战着礁石。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP5K20",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我记不清，是否曾在某处见过相似的场景。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP7K100",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我没有压抑怒火，而是选择释放它。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP7K101",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "威尔·安德森得到了巴德尔抑制剂，并许诺用它带来真正的光明。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP7K102",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我最终亲眼看到了何为“共振”，那是无限延伸的空间褶皱，\\n目光所及之处都如同泛着涟漪的水面般波动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP7K103",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我同时变成了无数个“我”，散布在星球的各个角落。\\n而“我”之中，又充满了“他们”。也许，不该再区分“我”和“他们”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP7K104",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里既不存在本质，也不存在形式，甚至没有“存在”本身。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtCH11EP7K105",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "静止而永恒，如梦一样美丽，也如梦一样易碎。\\n当出现思考与观察时，“我”从“他们”中被抽离出来……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtDLC2Trailer01",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "会员的肉体正在一点点变得透明。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtDLC2Trailer02",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "伴随着最后疯狂的叫喊，他完成了从实在向虚无的转变。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtDLC2Trailer03",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "他原先站立之处，最后只余下几件破损的衣物。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "TxtDLC3MST101",
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与此同时，雅卢岛另一侧的码头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
